#~ msgstr ""

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:73
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:94
msgctxt "H3"
msgid "Determining The Current Environment"
msgstr "判斷目前環境"

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:75
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:96
#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:102
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:107
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:103
msgctxt "P"
msgid "The current application environment is determined via the `APP_ENV` variable from your `.env` file. You may access this value via the `environment` method on the `App` [facade](/docs/{{version}}/facades):"
msgstr "網站目前的環境是通過 `.env` 檔中的 `APP_ENV` 變數來判斷的。可以通過 `App` [Facade](/docs/{{version}}/facades) 上的 `environment` 方法來存取這個值："

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:77
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:98
#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:104
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:109
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:105
msgctxt "CODE"
msgid ""
"use Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\App;\n"
"\n"
"$environment = App::environment();"
msgstr ""

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:81
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:102
#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:108
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:113
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:109
msgctxt "P"
msgid "You may also pass arguments to the `environment` method to determine if the environment matches a given value. The method will return `true` if the environment matches any of the given values:"
msgstr "可以傳入引數給 `environment` 方法來判斷目前環境是否符合給定的值。該方法會在目前環境符合任何一個給定值的時候回傳 `true`："

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:83
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:104
#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:110
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:115
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:111
msgctxt "CODE"
msgid ""
"if (App::environment('local')) {\n"
"    // The environment is local\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"if (App::environment(['local', 'staging'])) {\n"
"    // The environment is either local OR staging...\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:87
#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:93
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:98
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:94
msgctxt "P"
msgid "All of the variables listed in the `.env` file will be loaded into the `$_ENV` PHP super-global when your application receives a request. However, you may use the `env` function to retrieve values from these variables in your configuration files. In fact, if you review the Laravel configuration files, you will notice many of the options are already using this function:"
msgstr "在 `.env` 檔案中列出的所有變數都會在網站接收到請求的時候被載入進 `$_ENV` PHP 超全域變數內。不過，可以使用 `env` 函式來在設定檔中取得這些變數。事實上，若閱讀 Laravel 的設定檔，就會發現其中許多選項已經使用到這個函式了："

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:91
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:113
#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:119
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:124
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:120
msgctxt "P"
msgid "The current application environment detection can be overridden by defining a server-level `APP_ENV` environment variable."
msgstr "可以通過在伺服器等級上定義 `APP_ENV` 環境變數來複寫網站偵測到的應用程式環境。"

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:93
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:179
#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:185
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:190
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:186
#~ msgctxt "P"
#~ msgid "<a name=\"accessing-configuration-values\"></a>"
#~ msgstr ""

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:94
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:180
#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:186
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:191
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:187
msgctxt "H2"
msgid "Accessing Configuration Values"
msgstr "存取設定值"

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:96
msgctxt "P"
msgid "You may easily access your configuration values using the global `config` helper function from anywhere in your application. The configuration values may be accessed using \"dot\" syntax, which includes the name of the file and option you wish to access. A default value may also be specified and will be returned if the configuration option does not exist:"
msgstr "可以輕鬆的在專案內的任何地方通過 `config` 全域輔助函式來存取設定值。設定值可以通過「點」語法來存取，即包含設定檔名稱與欲存取的選項名。也可以指定設定選項不存在時要回傳的預設值："

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:98
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:184
msgctxt "CODE"
msgid ""
"$value = config('app.timezone');\n"
"\n"
"// Retrieve a default value if the configuration value does not exist...\n"
"$value = config('app.timezone', 'Asia/Seoul');"
msgstr ""

#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:100
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:105
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:101
msgctxt "H3"
msgid "Determining the Current Environment"
msgstr ""

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:103
msgctxt "P"
msgid "To set configuration values at runtime, pass an array to the `config` helper:"
msgstr "若要在執行階段修改設定值，可以傳入陣列進 `config` 輔助函式："

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:105
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:191
msgctxt "CODE"
msgid "config(['app.timezone' => 'America/Chicago']);"
msgstr ""

#: ./docs/8.x/configuration.md:107
#: ./docs/9.x/configuration.md:193
#: ./docs/10.x/configuration.md:205
#: ./docs/11.x/configuration.md:218
#: ./docs/master/configuration.md:214
